value: Resident and intra-African migrant, marshes: Ethiopia around Addis Ababa where present June - Sept; parts of E South Africa; records Zambia, Zimbabwe.
Highlands of Ethiopia and e South Africa
breeds shallowly, sometimes seasonally flooded, short dense grassland or marsh;in.South Africa in dense grass, sedges, & rushes averaging 1 m tall
